    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "That's a bit vague. You mentioned the 'power vacuum' and 'undermined interests,' but you also said it 'achieved its humanitarian aims.' If the end result was a failed state and a massive security hole in North Africa, shouldn't the intervention be classified as a strategic failure regardless of what happened to Gaddafi?",
